data.description: Show one Property for All Codepoints
data.name: Property
script
data.description: One or more ISO 15924 script codes separated by comma

data.name: properties
data.description: one or several key/value pairs of Unicode properties or int for decimal codepoint values or q for free text search.
Search for Codepoints. This API exposes the functionality of the main site’s search.
data.name: Search
action
data.description: the action to be applied to {data}, one of 'lower', 'upper', 'title', 'mirror', 'nfc', 'nfd', 'nfkc', 'nfkd'

data.name: data
data.description: The string to apply the transformation
Transform a String, e.g. , to upper-case, NFC, NFD, …
data.name: Transform

description: A RESTful Interface to Unicode Data, this API gives easy and standardized access to all information from Codepoints.net. The detailed documentation is [available on Github](https://github.com/Boldewyn/Codepoints.net/wiki/API).
